- 1 clock cycle to transition from `S_LOAD_INPUT` to `S_FIND_MAX`.
- N clock cycles to find the maximum value in the array of `N` elements.  
- 1 clock cycle to transition from `S_FIND_MAX` to `S_COUNT`.
